# Available system sounds on macOS:
# /System/Library/Sounds/Basso.aiff      - Deep error sound
# /System/Library/Sounds/Blow.aiff       - Soft whoosh
# /System/Library/Sounds/Bottle.aiff     - Pop sound
# /System/Library/Sounds/Frog.aiff       - Ribbit sound
# /System/Library/Sounds/Funk.aiff       - Funky beat
# /System/Library/Sounds/Glass.aiff      - Crystal chime
# /System/Library/Sounds/Hero.aiff       - Triumphant chord
# /System/Library/Sounds/Morse.aiff      - Morse code beep
# /System/Library/Sounds/Ping.aiff       - Classic ping
# /System/Library/Sounds/Pop.aiff        - Quick pop
# /System/Library/Sounds/Purr.aiff       - Cat purr
# /System/Library/Sounds/Sosumi.aiff     - Classic Mac sound
# /System/Library/Sounds/Submarine.aiff  - Sonar ping
# /System/Library/Sounds/Tink.aiff       - Light metallic sound

